    <file purpose="project-claude">projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7/CLAUDE.md</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §3 Sub-Agent Write Boundary">SEQUENTIAL — root `CLAUDE.md` writes happen only in main session.</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md Footer">"Every PR touching this file MUST add an entry to .claude/CHANGELOG.md." If we modify root CLAUDE.md, ALSO update `.claude/CHANGELOG.md`.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-08">No SUPERSEDED markers anywhere — if we add to §17 Pointers, the addition is clean.</constraint>
    <constraint source="conservative-default">Conservative — root CLAUDE.md is binding governance for every session. Only modify if R7 produced changes that warrant a pointer update.</constraint>
    <constraint source="dependency">Task 067 must have shipped — `ai-guide-consumer-wiring.md` must exist before §17 Pointers can cite it.</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §11">Cost-of-doing-nothing if NOT updated: future readers of root CLAUDE.md §17 can't easily find the new consumer-wiring guide. But this is mitigated because `PLAYBOOK-AUTHOR-GUIDE.md` (task 066) and `ai-architecture-actions-nodes-scopes.md` (task 062) both cross-reference the new guide.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <topic>documentation</topic>
    <files>
      <file>CLAUDE.md</file>
      <file>.claude/CHANGELOG.md</file>
      <file>docs/guides/ai-guide-consumer-wiring.md</file>
      <file>projects/spaarke-ai-platform-unification-r7/spec.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      Root CLAUDE.md is the binding instruction file loaded every session. §13 System Entry Points
      table maps subsystems → starting source files. §17 Pointers table maps topics → files. R7 might
      affect §17 (new consumer-wiring guide deserves a pointer) but is unlikely to affect §13 (BFF
      entry remains Program.cs). This task makes the explicit determination.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="067" status="not-started-but-required">ai-guide-consumer-wiring.md must exist before §17 can cite it.</dependency>
      <dependency task="060" status="not-started-but-required">Disposition list confirmed root CLAUDE.md is in Wave 6 scope (this task).</dependency>
